npc/damar: You made it through Stage 2. But this is a different place entirely.
npc/damar: Stage 2 was the surface web — visible, noisy, full of obvious traps. This is what runs underneath it.
npc/damar: The Cyber Network. Every server, every data pipe, every transaction moving gambling money in the middle of the night — it all passes through this layer.
npc/damar: The creatures here are Firewall Sentinels. They were not built to stop criminals. They were built to stop people like you — people who are trying to trace the signal back to its source.
npc/damar: They do not reason. They do not negotiate. They are pure enforcement logic running on corrupted infrastructure.
npc/damar: One more thing.
npc/damar: There is something else in this network. Something that was not always a machine.
npc/damar: Her name — or the name the system gave her — is the Collector. She is hunting in this layer right now.
npc/damar: If you hear something that sounds like a debt notice being read aloud... run.
